reviewText: I got this for my son for a Christmas present. He was very happy with it, but did say that it seems shorter than previous Slednecks movies (not as indepth).  There's lots of beautiful scenery and heart stopping snowmobiling going on in this movie!
Hated it. Great video but too many women in bikinis! Can't even watch with my kids! Very disappointed and shocked this can even be allowed!

Great video footage as always, and the KJ whitewater snowmobiling clip is almost worth it by itself (although no POV GoPro footage???). I have crossed a few rivers on my sled and have seen lake races, but that was ridiculous (in a good way).
